claim.claim-text:
1. A solid state imaging device comprising:
a light sensing part which conducts photoelectric conversion on incident light;
a ferroelectric layer including an organic compound on a surface of the light sensing part on which light is incident;
a transparent electrode formed on the ferroelectric layer;
a color filter layer formed on the transparent electrode; and
a condenser lens formed on the color filter layer.

8. The solid state imaging device according to claim 7, further comprising:
an interconnection layer formed under the semiconductor substrate;
a support substrate formed of a silicon substrate bonded to the bottom of the interconnection layer by an adhesive agent.
